{"tid":2277706,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【港講藝術】深夜時分，陪你看幾張杉本博司海景系列的攝影","createTime":"2020-11-08T16:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T16:48:47.000Z","uid":17335,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2817b67b28f9476efaaf15154a027e7e28bbffc7","tid":2277706,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T16:07:14.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\">攝影如何超越時間的限制，回到過去？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uji4qoT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuji4qoT.jpg&h=69abe660&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n早前談過杉本博司的「概念藝術」攝影，用一張相拍下整套兩小時的電影。這次則介紹Seascapes 《海景》系列，更加抽象，是有關人類記憶和遠古時間之作。<br />\n<br />\n《海景》是杉本博司一系列的攝影作品，數百張大氣與海洋 ，如此簡潔的畫面，幾乎千篇一律黑白灰，同時具有千變萬化的細節。這些海景卻有力地捕捉我們的目光，靜觀這些相片，彷彿能感悟禪意般的平和。<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FaWhLpW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFaWhLpW.png&h=cb0f1980&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n「從使用名為『攝影』的裝置以來，我一直想去呈現的東西，就是人類遠古的記憶。」<br />\n<br />\n「海景系列𥚃，我要處理的對象是水和大氣，這兩樣可說是至今為止對人而言變化最少的東西吧。」<br />\n<br />\n到底什麼是人類遠古的記憶 ？按杉本博司的說法，我們不妨可視地球上的動物植物，草樹山石，都會隨時而逝，唯獨海洋與天空的一線，億萬年恆久存在。這種不變，連接現在與遠古的海天之景，每張海景背後，都有屬於地球的原初印記。<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xWEbPRU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxWEbPRU.jpg&h=a07fd581&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n在傳統攝影 ，拍攝多數包含拍攝者的存在，張揚個己，但海景系列減去一切人、事、物，只留下純粹，只留下平靜、廣闊的海洋與天空。任何人類活動痕跡也沒有的存在狀態，此一概念，使攝影超脫了人為文化的連結。<br />\n<br />\n《海景》系列上追整個地球存在的歷史，將我們和遠古存在強烈地連繫起來，相中景象，和數十億年前的地球一樣，那時還未存在人類，甚至動植物都未誕生。<br />\n<br />\n杉本博司在時間與記憶之間，創作出極為具體而富有美感的藝術，淬煉出自古以來人類的共同記憶，甚至令觀者跨越時間的限制，回到遠古。<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F4GBgwZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF4GBgwZ.jpg&h=82c52f6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</p><br />\n1. Bay of Sagami, Atami, 1997<br />\n2. Mediterranean Sea, CassisDate, 1989<br />\n3. Bay of Sagami, Atami, 1997<br />\n5. Bay of Sagami, Atami, 1998"},{"pid":"fe325555f80ada501e4341db8f59888899827dea","tid":2277706,"uid":17335,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T16:09:17.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktsdjcC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktsdjcC.png&h=266b4478&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n 想睇更多文藝嘢，歡迎Follow德尼思化：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIG <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/delis.ver/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdelis.ver%2F&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq70v%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=6e1ec5a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/delis.ver/</a><br />\nFB <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Delisver.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDelisver.hk%2F&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq70v%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=497d158e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Delisver.hk/</a><br />\nMedium <a href=\"http://bit.ly/36HvepQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36HvepQ&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq70v%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=5066910a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/36HvepQ</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92a6cea8d94e09fa78549c4bd25f0ebcd24dc51","tid":2277706,"uid":258258,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T16:11:01.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n人係特別鐘意眺望大海、星晨<br />\n個意境好正"},{"pid":"d65a5d23d275a1314bd2f4ec5d88905c851db158","tid":2277706,"uid":247085,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T16:11:37.000Z","msg":"剩係得黑白，色盲？"},{"pid":"416059751af8